MARCSubfieldLabel: Edition statement (NR), Remainder of edition statement (NR)
Transformation Notes:
combine values, maintaining isbd punctuation. " = " indicates following string is a new value for subproperty "has designation of edition" <http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/m/P30133>. " / " indicates following string is a new value for subproperty "statement of responsibility relating to edition" <http://rdaregistry.info/Elements/m/P30121> 

If a reproduction condition is present, apply mapping and transformation to OriginalM, not ReproM. - LA, DC 2024-09-11
